      "content": "i know about the syndrome thing but he's already quite high and i dont have any calpol or nurofen here at the moment. he's really uncomfortable and i just want him to sleep. surely a couple of adult aspirin wouldn't be that dangerous if i just give him one or two to get him through the night?",
